OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fscattered showers, these more frequent
OL,8,Fover Dumfriesshire and the Southern
OL,9,FBorders. Drier in the southwest later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith just a few scattered showers,
OL,14,Fthese most likely in the morning.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fon Saturday with a few showers
OL,18,Fbreaking out. Dry much of Sunday then
OL,19,Frain spreading from northwest later,
OL,20,Flasting into Monday before brightening
OL,21,Fup later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
